improved_metadata.title: Sunshine Shirts (Squeegee Dance)
improved_metadata.description: This song celebrates the lively atmosphere of a screen printing shop, highlighting the team of Mike, Nick, and their park companions as they create vibrant shirts day and night. It's a tribute to the energy and rhythm of the printing process.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: Squeegee dance, highland beat, Park guys with, can't be beat
